        "heading": "Diagnostic pathway — red flags",
        "locator": "lines 182–189",
        "evidence_summary": "Lists chest pain, haemoptysis, cyanosis, inability to speak in sentences, confusion, unilateral leg swelling, stridor, rapid progression, and low oxygen saturation."
      },
