        "heading": "Key points — initial presentation, examination, and investigations",
        "locator": "lines 199–210",
        "evidence_summary": "Specifies onset and associated history, functional impact, exposures, medication context, vital signs, respiratory effort, cardiac and chest examination, and selected investigations."
